title: Coming into Our Power • EP210
itunes:title: Coming into Our Power • EP210
description:
This episode is pivotal for all of the characters.

 

Sophia and Joy really admire Peyton for using her art. Hilarie gets emotional remembering the personal significance of this episode and the pressure she put on herself to "get it right" when Peyton uses her art as protest in an unexpected way. 

 

Next, Felix & Brooke are Friends with Benefits. But... can FWB ever really work? Joy’s theory is that someone always loses an eye, but Hilarie has a different take
